          <a style="background-image:url('https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2016/05/j.brodkin-11_2.jpg');" class="author-photo" href="/author/jon-brodkin" tabindex="-1" role="presentation" aria-hidden="true"></a>
    
